metadata.name: Bananas for Cilantro
metadata.description:
A special piece for a special person. Banana Candy has created over 100 derivative pieces of artwork. But who creates derivates for him? This isn't a derivate just a homage to one of the greatest and kindest in the NFT game. This is just the beginning for this legend. 

If you're reading this you're almost too late.

Created by Immigrant Daughter for a great friend. 
An original cilantro doodle.
